# PingUp Admin System — Three-Tier RBAC + Full Dashboard

## Background

Building on the prior security audit, this plan upgrades from a flat single-role system to a **three-tier RBAC** with a **full admin dashboard** featuring analytics, trending content, moderation tools, and admin controls.

---

## Decisions (From Your Feedback)

| Question | Decision |
|----------|----------|
| Admin capabilities | Two-tier privileged roles: **MODERATOR** + **SUPER_ADMIN** |
| Dashboard design | Full layout: stats bar, charts (Recharts), trending, moderation, controls |
| First admin creation | **Env var** approach: `FIRST_ADMIN_EMAIL` in `.env` / application.properties |

---

## Role Hierarchy

| Role | Powers |
|------|--------|
| `USER` | Normal user — post, like, follow, message |
| `MODERATOR` | Hide/delete any post, mute users, view & act on reports |
| `SUPER_ADMIN` | All moderator powers + ban users, promote/demote mods, view analytics, manage hashtags |

