## Phase 4: Backend Admin Feature

### [MODIFY] `AuthService.java`
- `register()`: set `user.setRole("USER")` explicitly
- Both `register()` and `login()`: pass role to `generateToken(email, role)`

### [MODIFY] `DataSeeder.java`
- Read `FIRST_ADMIN_EMAIL` from `@Value("${app.admin.first-email:}")` 
- If set and user exists with that email → set role to `SUPER_ADMIN`
