### [NEW] `AdminService.java`
Implements all business logic for the above endpoints. Key methods:
- `getStats()` — counts from all repositories
- `getUserGrowthData(range)` — groups user signups by day
- `getPostActivityData(range)` — groups posts by day
- `getEngagementData(range)` — groups likes by day
- `getTrendingHashtags(range)` — top 10 from PostHashtag join
- `getViralProfiles(range)` — top by follower growth rate
- `getViralPosts(range)` — top 5 by like count
- `banUser(id)` / `muteUser(id)` — with self-protection guards
- `updateRole(id, role)` — validates role string, prevents self-demotion

