## Implementation Order

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Build in this exact order to avoid compilation failures at any step:

1. **Entities** — `Hashtag`, `PostHashtag`, `Report`, `BannedWord`, then modify `User`
2. **Repositories** — all 4 new + 4 modified
3. **Security** — `EntryPoint`, `AccessDeniedHandler`, modify `CustomUserDetailsService`, `JwtService`, `JwtAuthenticationFilter`
4. **Config** — `SecurityConfig`, `DataSeeder`, properties files
5. **DTOs** — `AdminDtos`, modify `UserResponse`, `Mapper`
6. **Services** — `AdminService`, modify `AuthService`
7. **Controllers** — `AdminController`, `ReportController`
8. **Frontend** — install Recharts, `api.js`, `admin.jsx`, `App.jsx`, `SideBar.jsx`

